13    /**
14    * Utility class used for efficient storage of {@link JsonToken}
15    * sequences, needed for temporary buffering.
16    * Space efficient for different sequence lengths (especially so for smaller
17    * ones; but not significantly less efficient for larger), highly efficient
18    * for linear iteration and appending. Implemented as segmented/chunked
19    * linked list of tokens; only modifications are via appends.
20    *<p>
21    * Note that before version 2.0, this class was located in the "core"
22    * bundle, not data-binding; but since it was only used by data binding,
23    * was moved here to reduce size of core package
24    */
